+
+- [x] **Stage 1: Route hooks** â€” POST bridge.registerAgent() + DELETE bridge.unregisterAgent() (FX001-1, FX001-2)
+- [x] **Stage 2: Notifier + DI** â€” Lazy bridge in notifier broadcastStatus() + DI factory wiring (FX001-3, FX001-4)
+
